# This app does NOT use server-side env vars for the Groq key.
# The user pastes their own key in the Settings modal and it persists to localStorage.
# The key is forwarded to Groq via the X-Groq-Key header on each request.
#
# Optional: set a default key for local dev only. Never ship with a key.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DEFAULT_GROQ_KEY=
